snippet.title: Dual Pong Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Dual Pong is now available on Itch!  You can also try out the free demo on the Web.

 

Dual Pong on Itch:
https://randomess-dj-p.itch.io/dual-pong  Dual Pong on the Web:
https://randomess-dj-p.itch.io/dual-pong-webgl-demo

For more info about this game, go to the link below.
http://paulmfullard.com/mygames.html
